	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64477189">I love playing games or watching shows that are post-future like Fallout or Horizon Zero Dawn where there's some ancient lost technology that are like magic to the main characters, and it's somehow 1,000 years old.  <p>

And then you look at the current world of planned obsolescence and how quickly technology devices degrade over time, and I wonder if that fantasy future will ever come to pass where my phone will last a thousand years.  What an amazing fantasy that is.</p></div>
	</div>

